race.comment: DRINK TIA (2) was out of the placings when seventh last time but prior to that produced an excellent 21.81 win over 380m at this track. Can measure up on top win two back. SWING SHIFT (1) finished well back at this track last time when a 6 length seventh (22.13) but scored five back at this track (21.61). Must be included in calculations. TOTAL FRANKY (5) produced a blistering 21.67 when winning over 380m at this track last start. Has the ability and can measure up again. JUDI STARLINE (8) has strong credentials over this journey.
